article.description: — Caleb Green scored 16 points as Fairfield got past Niagara 81-71 on Sunday.
article.headline: Green scores 16 to lift Fairfield over Niagara 81-71
article.linkText: Green scores 16 to lift Fairfield over Niagara 81-71
article.story: NIAGARA, N.Y. -- — Caleb Green scored 16 points as Fairfield got past Niagara 81-71 on Sunday. Zach Crisler had 14 points for Fairfield (5-3, 2-0 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Taj Benning added 13 points. Jesus Cruz had 11 points. Jordan Cintron had 14 points for the Purple Eagles (3-5, 0-2). Justin Roberts added 12 points. Marcus Hammond had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
